To be adopted, a submitted technology must include a PIM and at least one PSM; in addition, there must be an implementation or a commitment to provide an implementation within a year. Figure 6-6 shows three different views of the same application with its platform. The dashed lines enclose the parts of the technology that are, from the different viewpoints, considered to be the implementation of a platform.
